  "title": "CONSTRUCTION MANAGER CIVIL",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p>· Assist in planning and creating schedules and project timelines.</p>\n<p>· Overseeing and directing construction works from conception to completion</p>\n<p>· Coordinate and direct workers and subcontractors</p>\n<p>· Ensure quality construction standards and the use of proper construction techniques</p>\n<p>· Track deliverables, control subcontractors and suppliers to meet schedule, safety and quality objectives.</p>\n<p>· Planning of housekeeping by coordinating responsibilities of site engineers / site supervisors and sub-contractors.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<p>· Recognized Degree in Civil Engineering, with a minimum of 5 years experience in the Construction industry locally.</p>\n<p>· Strong leadership and supervisory skills</p>\n<p>· A team player with good communication skills</p>\n<p>· Meticulous and attentive to details</p>\n<p>· Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal</p>",
